room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
room_description: After a major breach in the agency security system, you've spent months on the trail of the double agent, but haven't gotten any closer to identifying the mole. In an effort to cover their tracks, the double agent has planted a bomb in the agency lab. Following the clues, you discover the device, but the countdown timer says there is only an hour left. Only quick thinking and resourcefulness will get you out of this explosive situation!
